  narrationText: {fileID: 0}
  narrationLines:
  - "\"I was just closing up for the night\u2026 just another shift."
  - "I don\u2019t remember falling asleep."
  - "But when I woke up\u2026 everything felt wrong."
  - "The halls are empty\u2026 the lights are dim\u2026"
  - And something is moving out there.
  - "I need to find a way out\u2026 now.\""
